Northern Foods Plc &lt;NFDS.L> said its&lt;Northserv Inc> unit had agreed to sell &lt;Flagship CleaningServices Inc> to &lt;Best Co Inc> of Nevada for 24.6 mln dlrscash.    Completion is due on April 30. Flagship is based inPhiladelphia and holds the Sears, Roebuck and Co &lt;S> franchisefor domestic carpet and upholstery cleaning throughout the U.S.    In the year to end March, 1986, Flagship - then known asKeyServ - reported pre-tax profits of 2.0 mln dlrs withend-year assets of 8.4 mln, giving a book profit on disposal of16.2 mln.    Northern Foods shares were unchanged at 297p. REUTER&#3;